articles.title: Visual Analytics Group 7 Project Site
articles.description: Welcome to the website. We hope you enjoy it!
articles.contents:
Hi, welcome to our group project website for visual analytics. Our group consist of Ting Yen-Hsin, He Qiyun and Ng Jianyuan Caine.
This project is about building a visual analytics app to analyze time series trend of sales at a chain of department stores. Please refer to respective sections for details.
